HEADWORD: Trunk steamer
<hw>Trunk steamer</hw>. <def>A freight steamer having a high hatch
coaming extending almost continuously fore and aft, but not of whaleback
form at the sides.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

